NosWings is an entire project, made by enthusiast people from different countries (Polish, German, Spanish, French...).
Our goal, is to bring the best NosTale private server people could ever imagine.
For that? We recruited the most talented folks all around the NosTale Community to get the best team to lead this project to the top.
The best server involves different sides: 
- New features;
- Balancing gameplay;
- Modernizing gameplay;
- Listening to players criticizm.
